This study evaluates the efficacy of Bifidobacterium breve CECT7263 and the mixture B.

 breve CECT7263/Lactobacillus fermentum CECT5716 in the treatment of infant colic.

 Group 1 will receive B.

 breve CECT7263 (2x10E8 CFU/day) one dose per day, group 2 will receive B.

 breve CECT7263 (1x10E8 CFU/day) and L.

 fermentum CECT5716 (1x10E8 CFU/day) in one dose per day, group 3 (control group) will receive simethicone 20 mg 4 times a day.

